body:
`hasRoot` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
  $search: {
    "index": "<index name>", // optional, defaults to "default"
    "hasRoot": {
      "operator": {
        <operator-specification>
      }
    },
    "returnScope": {
      "path": "<embedded-documents-field-to-retrieve>"
    },
    "returnStoredSource": true,
  }
}
```
